{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_20311.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story10","nameNarration":"杏子","narration":"还差一点……还差一点就能追上了！","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20311.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"narration":"好！追上了！"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"哗啦！"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"杏子","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"忧！你没事吧？"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101550}],"nameLeft":"忧","textLeft":"杏、杏子！@[chara:101550:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:101550:cheek_-1][chara:101550:motion_300][chara:101550:lipSynch_1]我刚才没办法游回来了……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":0}],"textRight":"嗯，你有好好浮着等我们来救你，@这就已经很棒了。"},{"chara":[{"id":101550,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"谢、谢谢！@因为我只擅长浮在水面上……"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"motion":100}],"textRight":"好，抓紧我，我们先回岸上去吧。"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":101550,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"嗯！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":260000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"（可现在水流太急，@根本没法回去……）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"（我可不想又被冲上无人岛！）"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200451,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnLast":2.5,"chara":[{"id":200451,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}],"turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"（沙耶香她到底在干嘛啊？）","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200451,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"chara":[{"id":200451,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}],"turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":200451,"mouthOpen":0}]},{"autoTurnLast":1.7,"chara":[{"id":200451,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"（她在朝旁边挥手……@意思是要我去旁边吗？）","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":260000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"textRight":"（啊，她是让我先离开水流啊！）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":260000,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200}],"textRight":"抓紧咯。","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101550,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"好、好的！"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":260000,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"杏子","textLeft":"呼……呼……@[chara:260000:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:260000:lipSynch_1]终、终于回来了……","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"id":260000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"（难道说我被冲到无人岛，@并不只是因为巨浪……）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"（还有刚才那些水流的缘故吗？）"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101550,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"忧","textRight":"杏子、沙耶香，对不起……","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200451,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"沙耶香","textLeft":"这不是你的错啦，你没事就好！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"杏子","textLeft":"今天就练习到这里吧。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":0}],"textRight":"诶！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"你都被冲走了啊？@难道你不害怕吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":300}],"textRight":"这、这……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101550,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"……"},{"chara":[{"id":101550,"lipSynch":1}],"textRight":"我当然害怕了……"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101550,"motion":0}],"textRight":"我也知道自己给你们添麻烦了……"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"那你还……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":400}],"textRight":"但是！"},{"chara":[{"id":101550}],"textRight":"我现在还游得不是很熟练……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200451,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"沙耶香","textLeft":"可你也不用那么着急啊？"},{"chara":[{"id":200451}],"textLeft":"明天让三日月别墅的人@教你不就好了。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":200}],"textRight":"明天就来不及了！@我一定要在今天之内学会。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200451,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":260000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"杏子","textLeft":"……"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":1}],"textLeft":"是有什么原因吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101550,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"……[wait:0.8][chara:101550:cheek_0][chara:101550:eyeClose_1][chara:101550:lipSynch_1]嗯。"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":101550,"motion":0}],"textRight":"因为我想去跳水……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"跳水？"},{"chara":[{"id":101550,"motion":100}],"textRight":"昨天姐姐她们……"},{"chara":[{"id":101550}],"textRight":"说我还不会游泳，@就不让我去跳水……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"（说起来……）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20281.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":110100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":101550,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"忧","textLeft":"姐姐，我也想玩那个！","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":110100,"motion":401}],"nameRight":"彩羽","textRight":"诶！？不、不可以！@你连游泳都不会呢！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_20251.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"杏子","textLeft":"（她们当时好像是起了争执。）","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":101550,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"忧","textRight":"跳水活动明天就要结束了吧？","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":200}],"textRight":"所以我一定要在明天之前学会游泳……"},{"chara":[{"id":101550}],"textRight":"让姐姐她们同意我去跳水。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200451,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"沙耶香","textLeft":"唔……但是……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":100}],"textRight":"求你们了！我差一点就能学会了。"},{"chara":[{"id":101550}],"textRight":"我马上就能满怀自信地@对姐姐她们说——"},{"chara":[{"id":101550}],"textRight":"哪怕是在深水区，我也能游泳了！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":260000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"杏子","textLeft":"……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":300}],"textRight":"如果现在打退堂鼓，@我就再也没有机会了……"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"（如果只是想在明天之前@“学会游泳”……）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"（那其实只要拜托御魂就好了……）"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"（可她想表达的@并不是这个意思吧。）"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":260000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"（而我……）"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"id":260000,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"……","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":260000,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"我知道了。"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story18","chara":[{"id":260000}],"textLeft":"你都说到这份上了，@那我就奉陪到底吧。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200451,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"沙耶香","textRight":"[chara:200451:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]咦！你居然会这么说！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"毕竟我之前都收了报酬嘛。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"忧","textRight":"啊！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200451,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"沙耶香","textRight":"嗯？这是弹珠？"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"忧，你要坚持到最后啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"忧","textRight":"嗯！杏子，谢谢你！"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":260000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"……"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20312.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":260000,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200451,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":260000,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"这是最后一次了！尽情地去游吧！","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":200451,"motion":201}],"nameRight":"沙耶香","textRight":"加油啊！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":260000},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200451}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101550,"motion":200,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"忧","textCenter":"嗯！我出发了！"},{"autoTurnLast":0.3,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":101550}],"textClear":1},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"哗啦！","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"fac